<h1>AMNI-CORE — PRIVACY POLICY</h1>
<p class="effective">Effective Date: March 3, 2026 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Last Updated: March 3, 2026</p>
<p>This privacy policy describes how Amni-Core, a systems platform developed by Amni-Scient ("we", "us", "our"), handles user information.</p>
<h2>1. DATA WE COLLECT</h2>
<p><strong>We collect no data.</strong> Amni-Core does not collect telemetry, usage data, crash reports, diagnostic information, or any form of personal data. No data is transmitted to Amni-Scient or any third party.</p>
<h2>2. DATA HANDLING</h2>
<p>Amni-Core operates at the hardware level. All system operations, storage management, and computational tasks execute locally on the hardware where it is installed. The platform has no built-in phone-home mechanism, update checker, or telemetry pipeline.</p>
<h2>3. THIRD-PARTY SERVICES</h2>
<p>Amni-Core does not integrate any third-party analytics, advertising, telemetry, or cloud services. The platform operates entirely independently once installed.</p>
<h2>4. DATA SHARING</h2>
<p>We do not share any data because we do not collect any data.</p>
<h2>5. SECURITY</h2>
<p>Amni-Core implements security at the systems level through a proprietary computational architecture designed for quantum resilience and GPU-forward execution. The platform employs a novel encoding scheme and memory model that operates fundamentally differently from conventional operating systems. Specific security mechanisms constitute proprietary trade secrets. The platform is designed to provide hardware-level isolation, integrity verification, and resistance to classes of attacks that exploit assumptions inherent in legacy system architectures.</p>
<h2>6. CHILDREN'S PRIVACY</h2>
<p>Amni-Core is a systems platform not directed at any specific age group. Since no data is collected, no special provisions apply.</p>
<h2>7. PERMISSIONS</h2>
<p>Amni-Core operates as a systems platform with hardware-level access by design. GPU access is integral to the platform's core execution model.</p>
<h2>8. CHANGES TO THIS POLICY</h2>
<p>We may update this privacy policy as the platform develops. The "Last Updated" date at the top will be revised accordingly.</p>
<h2>9. CONTACT</h2>
<p>For questions or concerns regarding this privacy policy:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:amnibro7@gmail.com">amnibro7@gmail.com</a></li>
